    <item>
      <title>欧洲公用事业公司达到17年的高度，关税Spark Haven搜索</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/europe-utilities-hit-17-year-high-as-tariffs-spark-haven-search</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税在全球范围内殴打股票，但投资者在欧洲公用事业中找到了避风港。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/europe-utilities-hit-17-year-high-as-tariffs-spark-haven-search</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 10:52:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中国对特朗普关税的报复，美国股票期货沉没</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/us-stock-futures-sink-as-china-retaliates-against-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股票期货在周五的早期交易中进一步跌跌撞撞，因为中国对所有美国进口的新美国关税进行了报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/us-stock-futures-sink-as-china-retaliates-against-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 10:43:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国以34％的美国商品关税对特朗普的关税打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/china-imposes-34-tariffs-on-all-us-imports-as-retaliation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国通过一系列措施对新的美国关税进行报复；包括对所有美国进出口的征税和稀土上的出口控制权；在唐纳德·特朗普总统施加职责并升级贸易斗争之后，兑现了罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/china-imposes-34-tariffs-on-all-us-imports-as-retaliation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 10:10:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股票负责纠正后，中国关税应对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/european-stocks-extend-drop-set-for-worst-week-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中国对美国关税的报复，欧洲股票下降，并进行更正，并进一步升级了全球贸易战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/european-stocks-extend-drop-set-for-worst-week-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 07:21:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普关税冲击从记录中抛售时，黄金降低了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/gold-steadies-after-us-tariff-shock-sparks-selloff-from-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）更具侵略性的关税议程之后，戈德（Gold）远离了其最新纪录的最新纪录，席卷了悲观的情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/gold-steadies-after-us-tariff-shock-sparks-selloff-from-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 00:05:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油在关税和欧佩克供应量受到打击的三年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石油跌落了第二天，由于交易者消化了欧佩克+的惊喜产量增加，并迅速升级了全球贸易战争，因此在三年多的时间内下降到最低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 22:53:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>S＆amp; p 500期货潜水3％作为抛售增长势头：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股票期货跌倒了，表明华尔街又遭受了巨大的损失，随着中国开始在全球贸易战争的下一个阶段，债券与美国产品的新关税开始。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 22:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当关税颠覆全球增长时，Dollar会在Trump集会后删除</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/dollar-wipes-out-post-trump-rally-as-tariffs-upend-global-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）于11月赢得总统职位以来，由于全球市场的新浪潮使全球市场赢得了总统职位以来，美元已经消除了所有收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/dollar-wipes-out-post-trump-rally-as-tariffs-upend-global-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 20:05:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Zloty沉没时，波兰政策制定者的眼睛半点降低了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/polish-central-bank-chief-stumps-markets-with-pivot-to-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名波兰政策制定者下个月的利率下降了多达50个基点，这是央行中央银行州长亚当·格拉平斯基（Adam Glapinski）出乎意料地转向货币宽松的第二天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/polish-central-bank-chief-stumps-markets-with-pivot-to-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 17:19:22 GMT</pubDate>
